  %p
    There are many ways to engage with the Jenkins project and community. Here are the most common ways to get you
    started. Welcome aboard!
  .grid-container
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-meet
      .content
        %h3 MEET
        %p Meet other Jenkins users and share your experiences by organizing and attending events and meetups.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-meet{:href => "/participate/meet", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-code
      .content
        %h3 CODE
        %p Do you enjoy writing code? There are numerous plugins and components for you to contribute to.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-code{:href => "/participate/code", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-help
      .content
        %h3 HELP
        %p As an experienced user, you can help others get the most out of Jenkins.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-help{:href => "/participate/help", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-translate
      .content
        %h3 TRANSLATE
        %p If you're fluent in languages other than English, consider improving support for those languages.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-translate{:href => "/doc/developer/internationalization/", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-test
      .content
        %h3 TEST
        %p You can help prevent regressions by contributing automated tests.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-test{:href => "/participate/test", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-document
      .content
        %h3 DOCUMENT
        %p Improve the documentation to make it easier for others to get started.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-document{:href => "/participate/document", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-design
      .content
        %h3 DESIGN
        %p As it is intended for daily use by finicky web developers, design is essential
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-design{:href => "/participate/design", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
    .card
      .bg-img.bg-img-review
      .content
        %h3 REVIEW
        %p Help review changes to code or documentation.
        %br/
        %br/
        %a.btn.btn-review{:href => "/participate/review-changes", :style => " position:absolute;                  \nbottom:8.6%;                          \nleft:4.4%; "} Read More
  %p.channels-help
    %b
      Help and feedback.
    Please contact us in the
    %a{:href => "https://gitter.im/jenkinsci/newcomer-contributors"}
      Newcomer
    or
    %a{:href => "https://gitter.im/jenkinsci/advocacy-and-outreach-sig"}
      Advocacy and Outreach SIG
    channels if you have any questions about contributing to Jenkins.
    Any feedback about the guidelines will be appreciated.
